TextIt,is,a,service,for,building,SMS,applications,It,is,designed,to,help,people,who,are,not,programmers,create,and,modify,SMS,applications,using,the,visual,interactive,Flow,engine,Once,created,users,can,launch,their,applications,in,any,country,using,their,Android,phones,TextIt,s,REST,API,allows,users,to,access,their,Android,relayers,from,outside,applications,Specifically,users,can,handle,contacts,create,new,messages,manage,Android,phones,manage,calls,list,active,flows,and,start,flow,runs